        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4 font-heading text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">
          What Makes KOHO Special?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          KOHO represents a fundamental shift in Canadian banking. While traditional banks profit from fees and
          penalties, KOHO is built around helping you succeed financially. With features like instant cashback,
          automatic savings, real-time budgeting tools, and credit building—all without monthly fees—KOHO puts your
          financial wellness first.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Our Commitment to You -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4 font-heading text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">
          Our Commitment to You
        </h3>
        <div class="text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed space-y-4">
          <p>
            We're committed to providing accurate, up-to-date information about KOHO's features, benefits, and
            promotional offers. Our team stays informed about the latest updates to ensure you always have access to the
            most current information.
